\
Across all research, one conclusion is consistent:\
\
- Preventable diseases are a major cause of early death  \
- Vaccination significantly reduces this risk  \
- Adherence to schedules is critical for effectiveness  \
\
Therefore:\
\
**Any system that improves vaccination adherence  \
can indirectly increase pet lifespan.**\
\
---\
\
## Positioning Opportunity\
\
Products that:\
\
- Track health records  \
- Provide reminders  \
- Enable easy vaccination access  \
\
Are not just convenience tools.\
\
They are:\
\
**Preventive healthcare systems that improve survival outcomes.**\
